Problem 6: Loan Eligibility
Take:
• Monthly income
• Age
Conditions:
• Age between 21 and 60
• Income ≥ 25000
Print whether the person is eligible for a loan.

#!/bin/bash
read -p "monthly income : " income
read -p "monthly age : " age
if [ $income -ge 25000 ] && [ $age -ge 21 ] && [ $age -le 60 ]; then
        echo "eligible"
else
        echo "Not eligible"
fi